This directory contains two subdirectories: atangle and aweave,
which contains the ada code for same.

It also contains the files:

awebmac.tex:	The TeX macro
		file needed for processing the output of the aweave processor
		into beautiful documentation.

awebman.tex:    The aweb documentation in TeX format.

awebman.ps:	The aweb documentation in PostScript format.


To build the aweb programs with GNAT, cd to the respective directory
and type "gnatmake aweave" or "gnatmake atangle".  

